org.aksw.fox.data

Class EntityClassMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aksw.fox.data.EntityClassMap

  • public class EntityClassMap
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains constants to map the entity type/class for each NER tool. The types/classes are used in FOX are L, O, P, M and N.
    Author:
    rspeck
